prompt: Lav en maskine, der suger kvælstof ud af havet og puster det ind i flotte balloner, man kan købe til fødselsdagsfester
author: Victor
revisedPrompt: Create an image of an imaginative contraption, designed to extract nitrogen from the sea, and subsequently inflate it into beautiful balloons. Display these balloons in an array of radiant colors and patterns, making them an irresistible purchase for birthday parties. The machine should be intricate and appealing, inspiring amazement and curiosity from onlookers, just as much as the balloons it produces
